description	"Zaalbar

Class: Mandalorian.
Class Summary: 
A low defense, high offense melee weapon user. 

Weaponry:
- Vibro-Weapon *
- Sonic pistol *
- Bowcaster (3)
- Fire Grenades (3)
- Heavy Melee

* Special Weapon Descriptions:  
--- Vibro-Weapon 
- Defense (1)
- Can block lightsabers, cannot block blaster fire
- Slightly increased damage compared to lightsaber
- Vibroblade uses Yellow style and has the longest reach 
- Dual Vibroswords use Dual style and increased swing speed

--- Sonic Pistol
- Based on Pistol level 1
- Applies sonic stun effect on successful hits
- 2 shots per clip

Attributes:
- Runs faster in melee
- Blast Armor
- Strength (3) *
--- Cannot be slapped or knocked down by explosions

Zaalbar was the son of Wookiee Chieftain Freyyr, but had been exiled from his homeworld."

